Class PlayerLevelUpEvent

java.lang.Object
events.models.PlayerLevelUpEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
Event, Serializable
public class PlayerLevelUpEvent extends Object implements Event
The PlayerLevelUpEvent class implements the Event interface. This class is responsible for carrying out the leveling up of the player during gameplay.
